{"tid":442471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報復美國 北韓封殺facebook twitter","createTime":"2017-10-20T16:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T06:03:24.000Z","uid":144372,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"89cd46a9ec39bb43ff6d505cd123acab625712d9","tid":442471,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20160401/54935412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20160401%2F54935412&d=WlE0%2BH1Q2bB1Sc%2BZ6rwjmXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=893fa838\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20160401%2F54935412&h=8f14ad07\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20160401/54935412</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓進一步收緊控制網上資訊流通。郵政及電訊部門正式宣佈，封殺社交網facebook、YouTube、Twitter以及南韓網站。<br />\n<br />\n郵電部在國營流動服務供應商Koryolink及其他互聯網供應商貼出告示，指「反對北韓的虛假宣傳網站、色情成人網站」連同多個國際社交網全被封鎖。這些社交網過去數月已經非正式被封殺，到周五從平壤無法進入。<br />\n北韓只有少數人可以使用到互聯網，一般人只能使用受政府局限的內聯網，但過去外國人是可以自由瀏覽的。"},{"pid":"22cceae699a8532441a84ea3b08e01601db05d24","tid":442471,"uid":138474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ac06a2cb062863971cbd3a9323035028560c34","tid":442471,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"480ec1466489d236e819b7be7455cb4487224bb0","tid":442471,"uid":144372,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果邊D人連小米機都買唔起<br />\n點樣上facebook twitter?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲小米<br />\n大米都買唔起啦"},{"pid":"d97091ad3cd7b45a32651d44a41981b70282c776","tid":442471,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0